OL,5,G2100 Bangers & Cash
OL,6,     FCortina/Austin Campervan: As a
OL,7,     Fteenager, all Dave wanted for his
OL,8,     Ffirst car was a 2 litre Ghia
OL,9,     FCortina, and today he's off to
OL,10,     FNottinghamshire to collect just
OL,11,     Fthat, alongside a Mark 1 Capri.
OL,12,G2200 Bangers & Cash
OL,13,     FFord Capri Consort: A rare 1964
OL,14,     FFord Capri Consul coupe comes up
OL,15,     Ffor auction. Paul takes a 1957
OL,16,     FLeyland Comet truck for a spin,
OL,17,     Fand Dave admits that high on his
OL,18,     Fwish-list is a Citroen 2CV.
